Key Match Events: Yusei Kikuchi finished six innings for the first time as an Astro and with 12 strikeouts fell one shy of matching his season high
Pre-Game Insights: The Astros have won all six games Yusei Kikuchi has started, including a 5-2 victory against the Royals on Saturday night
Post-Match Reflections: Dana Brown said that Kikuchi has afforded stability to a rotation that had little to speak of
Brown said that they hope the final report card on Kikuchi is good
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Astros have a season-high 13 games above.500
Ben Gamel has started 10 of the Astros' 11 games since they claimed him off waivers from the New York Mets
Others: The Astros have made seven waiver claims this season, a response to their spate of pitching injuries and outfield underperformance
